        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Keltská osada 3D"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nPredstavujeme Vám našu novú 3D vizualizáciu. Tento krát sa jedná o idealizovanú predstavu keltského sídliska z územia južného Slovenska. Kelti okrem väčších zrubových domov používali podobné polozemnice ako poznáme neskôr u Slovanov, boli však väčšie a líšili sa niektorými detailmi.&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhv7OZuWS4RX4ng1ckBZv5YVov4o9-tBIswu47bS_lpUHpvy7RosiNtgCRusAnHHbjn0EEburJiLCehLFFNOKMrF9fltpVRgQ9Elm1-IEmjvAxkoYEIWZOd-NOmI85yakrGGNlZyUfOXyg/s1600/dom.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"900\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhv7OZuWS4RX4ng1ckBZv5YVov4o9-tBIswu47bS_lpUHpvy7RosiNtgCRusAnHHbjn0EEburJiLCehLFFNOKMrF9fltpVRgQ9Elm1-IEmjvAxkoYEIWZOd-NOmI85yakrGGNlZyUfOXyg/s320/dom.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nDomy s mazanicovou „omietkou“ mohli mať  steny zafarbené a dokonca s maľovanou výzdobou. Použili sme tiež typickú keltskú keramiku, zbrane, či tkáčsky stav. Prechádzka po keltskej dedine starej 2000 rokov má jedinečnú atmosféru.&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"YOUTUBE-iframe-video\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/xvJt3ZmRpCM/0.jpg\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"266\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xvJt3ZmRpCM?feature=player_embedded\" width=\"320\"></iframe></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nZa odbornú pomoc ďakujeme archeológom Radovanovi Čambalovi a Branislavovi Kovárovi.<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiB3qWS9nX7vhUVuLTmP0QPS64I3EOvZX-eIua4b8q3MDyRKCeqJE46Fz6BJwTi7RX42_SvUfYnQfSARGItTPP2fDq_ATa66fODqr33D__8M8NTygNDwTh12r-H4NcjdiV-YjZLZzc_PC4/s1600/21688373_1972249446383885_248919233811076886_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"900\" data-original-width=\"1600\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiB3qWS9nX7vhUVuLTmP0QPS64I3EOvZX-eIua4b8q3MDyRKCeqJE46Fz6BJwTi7RX42_SvUfYnQfSARGItTPP2fDq_ATa66fODqr33D__8M8NTygNDwTh12r-H4NcjdiV-YjZLZzc_PC4/s320/21688373_1972249446383885_248919233811076886_o.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgDNu5-8JRHkxgNnOXqptJRJ9Tvpt4dKkJXykXM0nhKUsYJSK6qqgceL_5M-RUP7yEgWvjXMRO19jVX3wDSTp6DaU2Gx9qhzgDUqUXR_g0m11ZAslJ_122IWqCIAKB48Q65g1NhiDC1yQA/s1600/21762537_171380146745898_356741393756732363_o.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"640\" data-original-width=\"1137\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgDNu5-8JRHkxgNnOXqptJRJ9Tvpt4dKkJXykXM0nhKUsYJSK6qqgceL_5M-RUP7yEgWvjXMRO19jVX3wDSTp6DaU2Gx9qhzgDUqUXR_g0m11ZAslJ_122IWqCIAKB48Q65g1NhiDC1yQA/s320/21762537_171380146745898_356741393756732363_o.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEi0XfvrS_12lTYU8GJgNLC0uhlqxNtWjJon6-pez3C1D4eN6iuwonMtPEgVaqHcrn-h3s0xoLZUfZ1yQ5CoLNh25qykBzdJhEU_MvZ